message.body: WELCOME TO MY LIFE DURING BREAK! And slightly right now.... Why?
Sheridan you know how you sometimes think you might like a boy who's your friend but you're not really sure and you can't really tell if it's flirting or friendship?

Omg. I must be going insane. This editing is making me crazy... Because I can't. I don't... I don't really like B, do I? Because that would really make things so complicated. I don't even know what I'm talking about but I'm freaking out. This is not good.
Okay Jenna, calm down... Do you want me to call you? Or will I wake people up?
Yes! Dude if you have time. Or I'm not keeping you up or you're busy
Hello poppet, how are you holding up?
My whole life is a lie.
Yes dear! Was in a meeting! I'll write you as I'm on the subway home:)
Oh Jenna, my dear. What is life without love? Without people to share it with

And on top of all of that, I'm now beginning to see that I've basically turned a blind eye to anything that did not pertain to achieving my dream of filmmaking and I've hurt a lot of people and missed a lot of experiences in the process... And it's breaking my heart and I'm terrified this will be my undoing
